<style>
body {
  font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  background-color: #99CCB3;
}

.order_number {
  color: #DE5E35;
  padding: 5px;
  border: 1px dashed #DE5E35;
  border-radius: 3px;
}

.email_text {
  width: 40rem;
  background-color: #F7FBF9;
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
  margin: 1rem auto;
}
</style>

<div class="email_text">
  <p style="font-weight:bold">Hello <%= @user.first_name.capitalize %></p>

  <p>Thank you for ordering from <%= @order.restaurant.name %> with Vegan Wheels.</p>

  <p style="font-weight:bold">Your order number is: <span class="order_number"><%= @order.id %></span></p>

  <p>Your expected delivery time is <span style="font-weight:bold"><%= (@order.order_time + 30.minutes).strftime("%l:%M %p") %></span></p>

  <p>Please note that restaurants sometimes receive more orders than usual. This means that your delivery may arrive later than specified. You can see the status of your order on your <%= link_to "dashboard", dashboard_index_url %>.</p>

  <p>When you see your order has been collected by a rider, your meal should be with you in no longer than 20 mins. Weâ€™ll do our best to keep you updated either by phone or text if either we or the restaurant you ordered from are expecting delays with your meal.</p>

  <p>See you soon,</p>
  <p>Veganwheels x</p>
</div>